This is my personal to-do-list for every release:

 1. Check README.md for changes
 2. Update Changelog
 3. Update version in cournal/__init__.py
 4. git commit -a
 5. git tag v0.x
 6. git push --tags
 7. ./setup.py sdist
 8. Upload release tarball
 9. Update ebuild
10. Update PKGBUILD
11. Test!!!
12. Upload new ebuild and AUR
13. Update gtk-apps.org
14. Update website?
15. Update sourceforge
16. Send ML announcement
17. Close github milestone

18. Bump version in cournal/__init__.py to prerelease
19. Update ChangeLog for next release
